      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:35:2",
      "text": [
        " لَا يُقْطَعُ يَدُ السَّارِقِ إِلَّا فِي شَيْ‏ءٍ تَبْلُغُ قِيمَتُهُ مِجَنّاً وَ هُوَ رُبُعُ دِينَارٍ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "From him, from Abdullah Bin Sinan, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The hand of the thief would not be cut regards to anything except if it reaches the value of a <span class=\"iTxt\">Mijanna</span>, and it is a quarter of a Dinar’."
        ]
      }
